// --- README.md ---
# Java Pocket Tutor üìò
A simple, clean, offline-ready mobile tutorial app that teaches Java
concepts through bite-sized lessons.

## Features
- Complete set of 10 foundational Java lessons
- Syntax-highlighted code blocks for readability
- Fully offline and built with Jetpack Compose UI

## Tech Stack
- Kotlin (Android)
- Jetpack Compose
- Local lesson repository

## License
MIT

